# Contractor API Endpoint - POST with FluentValidation violation (admin name)
POST http://localhost:5134/api/contractor
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "admin"
}

###
# Contractor API Endpoint - PATCH with name exceeding MaxLength
PATCH http://localhost:5134/api/contractor/1
Content-Type: application/json-patch+json

[
  { "op": "replace", "path": "/name", "value": "New Contractor New Contractor New Contractor New Contractor New Contractor New Contractor New Contractor New Contractor New Contractor New Contractor New Contractor New Contractor New Contractor New Contractor New Contractor"
  }
]

